# Title: UAC Bypass WSReset
# Author: Christian Burkard (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2021-08-23
# Level: high
# Description: Detects the pattern of UAC Bypass via WSReset usable by default sysmon-config
# MITRE Tactic: Privilege Escalation
# Tags: attack.privilege-escalation, attack.t1548.002
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_uac_bypass_wsreset_integrity_level.yml

Image="*\\wsreset.exe" IntegrityLevel IN ("High", "System", "S-1-16-16384", "S-1-16-12288")